      ],
      "start": 9.8,
      "text": "It is currently 24 degrees and partly cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 18.1,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 15.24,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "afdd36e5083"
      ],
      "end": 31.44,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 18.68,
      "text": "NVIDIA and LG Group are building a new AI factory to accelerate physical AI. The facility will provide accelerated computing infrastructure for robotics, autonomous driving, and GPU cloud services."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a0e99837603"
      ],
      "end": 54.27,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s4",
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 31.44,
      "text": "While industry infrastructure expands, political stability remains fragile in other regions. In Armenia, Prime Minister Nikol Pashinyan has secured a victory, but the election was marred by extreme polarisation and hate speech. Dr. Narek Sukiasyan describes these conditions as signs of democratic backsliding within the country."
    },
    {
      "end": 57.13,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 54.61,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 64.85,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 57.47,
      "text": "This afternoon will be partly cloudy with no rain expected and temperatures between 24 and 25 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 73.2,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "calendar_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 64.85,
      "text": "And from the weather, a quick look at the calendar."
    },
    {
      "end": 80.0,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "calendar",
      "segments": [
        "s11",
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 73.2,
      "text": "On your calendar today: Your work calendar has a department retro all day and an AP2 meeting at nine in the morning. Your personal calendar has Twerchhau at seven in the evening."
    },
    {
      "end": 82.56,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s13"
      ],
      "start": 80.16,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 88.76,
      "id": "p9",
      "index": 9,
      "section_index": 9,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s14"
      ],
      "start": 83.8,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 94.44,
